{"tid":1764923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿富汗文物館因為黑警叫停在港展覽","createTime":"2019-12-01T12:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T13:56:41.000Z","uid":252132,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ded0c8c67b70ce70e4d33a4dc022b7d090ddf7","tid":1764923,"uid":252132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"黑警入左歷史博物館 搞到人地阿富汗文物局叫停咗個展<br />\n<br />\nFrom fb <br />\n原Po: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yhmetblogspot/photos/a.988877534495718/2812459252137528?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyhmetblogspot%2Fphotos%2Fa.988877534495718%2F2812459252137528%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B0B1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=611a2e7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yhmetblogspot/photos/a.988877534495718/2812459252137528?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n/還記得堂堂飛虎隊被人逮到在歷史博物館執勤時睇鹹片，結果反控職員阻差辦公嗎？港警擅闖博物館令阿富汗文物局大為震驚，保安不滿2000年歷史的國寶、貴霜帝國的王妃金冠及多件文物受威脅，決定叫停展覽。香港這個所謂的國際城市，就這樣被一個烽火國度摑了一巴。港警的惡名昭彰程度，看來比阿蓋德還要差，實在有辱國體。/ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/01/204239_a3c2c34dcbc3ccf5d77d25b77b920afe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F01%2F204239_a3c2c34dcbc3ccf5d77d25b77b920afe.png&h=2d0c3cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正苦就唔敢同人講係柒到比人叫停，淨係話特殊社會狀況，popo 連文化界都搞埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CD2SLb4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCD2SLb4.png&h=861595e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.history.museum/zh_TW/web/mh/exhibition/current.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.history.museum%2Fzh_TW%2Fweb%2Fmh%2Fexhibition%2Fcurrent.html&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B0B1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=f4931b6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.history.museum/zh_TW/web/mh/exhibition/current.html</a>"},{"pid":"cfd462ddf5541747c20c2703fcfbab200e3a7a41","tid":1764923,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:51:51.000Z","msg":"推到有真相"},{"pid":"78209ef1f6b5e888ba41b43830ee80285fefc7d2","tid":1764923,"uid":321050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:56:26.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位promote下。香港人贏唔贏靠尼個：<br />\n<br />\n非建制區議員平台<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1764928\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1764928</a>"},{"pid":"126561ebf49780fef8b791e557c266d1704190fc","tid":1764923,"uid":73611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:40:33.000Z","msg":"堅定流？"},{"pid":"23ff9f2281cb71d01bb15a8c0d6817ae24a261f9","tid":1764923,"uid":65178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:54:14.000Z","msg":"蒙面曱甴醜出國際 屌你老母"},{"pid":"3016a5b56b49d2b65e2bb60fcea327e60a94e3fb","tid":1764923,"uid":137038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:56:41.000Z","msg":"講真，如果好似之前科學館有木乃伊睇，然後有綠色曱甴出沒，我諗英國佬都會好擔心"}]}